Subject: Re: [VB] How to remove crank pulley??

If you have one of those aluminum aftermarket units, gently heat the center 
of the pulley until it slides off. Aluminum expands at a greater rate than 
the steel crank. Prolly doesn't work on the standard steel units.

Chris 
